#: src/callbacks.c:137
msgid ""
"Ground plane detected in model. T_ant results will overcount ground effects. "
"Free-space models are standard for antenna temperature evaluation."
msgstr ""
"Bidang ground terdeteksi dalam model. Hasil T_ant akan menghitung berlebih "
"efek ground. Model ruang bebas adalah standar untuk evaluasi suhu antena."

#: src/callbacks.c:153
#, c-format
